title: Test
summary: This grouped bar chart has 4 categories of Quarter on the x axis representing 2 groups: 2016, and 2017.
Averaging these 2 groups, the highest category is found for Quarter Q1 with a mean value of 258.5.
Followed by Q4 with a mean value of 194.5.
The lowest category is observed at Q3 that has a mean value of 175.0
showing a difference of 38.5% with the maximum value.
In case of Q4, 2016 shows more dominance than any other Quarter and it has the lowest value in Q1.
